 PARTITION BY clause :- 
 ====================

  => partition by claue is used to divide the based on one or more columns.

  => used to find ranks with in group.

  => for ex to find ranks with in dept first divide the table dep wise and apply 
       rank / dense_rank function on each dept

  Ex :- 
 
  SQL>BREAK ON DEPTNO SKIP 1 

 SQL> SELECT deptno,ename,sal,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY deptno ORDER BY sal DESC)  as rnk
          FROM emp ;

